    General Stores in Kanjurmarg, Mumbai

    General Stores in Kanjurmarg, Mumbai

    In India, general stores or mom-n-pop shops are generally referred to as 'kiranas'. In marketing terminology, a kirana shop is a form of traditional retail catering to the needs of citizens. In certain metros and cities, a general store can also be a part of a pharmacy or medicine shop. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. The vast list of general store items does not limit to food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Catering to the convenience of their customers, these shops also extend free home delivery service. These store owners work in conjunction with wholesalers, distributors, and retailers forming a wide network in the city or town. You can find one from a large number of General Stores in Kanjurmarg, Mumbai from the list given above.
